{"tid":657407,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Dark Souls溝PUBG再溝Bloodborne新Game 《Egress》","createTime":"2018-05-08T05:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T03:51:56.000Z","uid":9031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5907299236d2cb29840986c46cbe0abf40943f8c","tid":657407,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r0RsNS6-kQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr0RsNS6-kQw&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=3584e1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r0RsNS6-kQw</a><br />\n<br />\n開發商Fazan Games日前公佈了一段旗下新作《出口》（Egress）的影片，向玩家展示了本作的玩家對戰玩法。<br />\n<br />\n《出口》在今年2月份正式公佈，是一款大逃殺玩法結合上類似&ldquo;魂系列&rdquo;的戰鬥系統。遊戲背景結合了&ldquo;維多利亞時代&rdquo;以及&ldquo;克蘇魯神話&rdquo;（致敬《血源詛咒》？），玩家需要在錯綜複雜的維多利亞風城鎮中搜尋探索，並打到地圖上的其他玩家。<br />\n<br />\n從本次公開的影片中也可以看出，遊戲無論是在攻擊動作還是翻滾閃避亦或是鎖定上都與&ldquo;魂系列&rdquo;的戰鬥相當類似，遊戲攻擊方式除了近戰以外，還有槍械、投擲道具以及魔法攻擊。從界面右邊的玩家數量來看，一局遊戲至少支持22名玩家同場。<br />\n<br />\n《出口》2018年內登陸PS4、Xbox One、PC平台。<br />\n<br />\n炒埋一碟做瀨尿牛丸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7d1db3b4d199d48d15fd3d5f8a06d5f7c8a237","tid":657407,"uid":82749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯"},{"pid":"a24312a7772fc89b40e126a14304d9b4e26a48d8","tid":657407,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2ab3abaef0e018df154099cf52d70861df8833","tid":657407,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"依家D GAME都係左抄抄右抄抄架啦"},{"pid":"e254aaf1733ff66ac440f0162b6c4bf5304f9b34","tid":657407,"uid":48222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"啲打擊感完全冇FEEL，好冇力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi